-- Switchblade --

Switchblade keeps dragging the unconcious Perceptor and eventually 
ends up in the control room. He struggles to prop up the dead weight 
against the wall. Them he reactivates Perceptor, and jumps 
backwards, just in case.

"Nightstrike, make sure that there are no suvivors. Firestrike, 
where are you?" says Swithblade as he waits for a response from 
Perceptor.
